@ Touchmetal .....lets see if ive got this straight.....its free music.....its a fast download..... all tracks are tagged correctly....but your still not happy.

But if you say the songs are tagged i believe you.You are a VIP so obv you make quality stuff.I suppose its possible the problem is at my end.I am really sorry for my earlier comment...

Keep up the good work...
